atness or to increase your contribution level.&nbsp; Thank you!</span><br /><br /></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium;">Just click this <strong><a href="Documents/lds-philanthropies/Together For Greatness/T4G Employee Fillable Form 2012.pdf">T4G Donation&nbsp;Form</a></strong> and fill in the information for Payroll Deduction.&nbsp; </span><span style="font-size: medium;">If you would like to make just a one-time donation, click&nbsp;<strong><a href="https://donate.byui.edu/TNHO3ajmoEyyUA7Sb5uKkg/G/5ZgVo9Qd8EmHpj8ZRnFhzg?cat=vfYRMDKvE0aexKqLdqO31Q&amp;cde1=646">here</a></strong>.&nbsp; <br /></span><span style="font-size: medium;"><br />Sign the form and send it to:&nbsp;<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br /><br /></span><strong>Together for Greatness&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />LDS Philanthropies<br />1216 Stocks Avenue<br />Brigham Young University-Idaho<br />Rexburg, ID&nbsp; 83460-1657&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br /><br /><br /></strong>"As department chair and now as dean, I have seen the direct results of participating in Together for Greatness. Resources made available through the program greatly enhance the quality of experience for students and employees at BYU-Idaho. &nbsp;In some cases, such opportunities would otherwise not be available or greatly limited. Thank you for joining me as a participant and contributor."&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong><strong>Kevin Brower<br /></strong></strong>&nbsp;</p>
